Body: Description: Hi, Within the 'resource owners' section, when i select to Add and owner manually, I can input the site that I want but when I get to 'select owners' I am only seeing 'ICT' domain. Whereas previously I could see multiple domains. I can therefore only security an owner in ICT domain which should not be the case. This is a new issue and I was able to select from our multiple domains in the past.
What We've Learned Updated: AD Scan was faulting
Next Steps Updated: Run AD Scan correctly
What We've Learned Updated: Domains were missing in the "AuthSearchDomain" field in the "AccessInformationCenter.Service.exe.config" file
